---
title: Mexican-Inspired Chorizo Tortilla Stacks with Fresh Salsa and Lime Crema
description: What's better than a quesadilla? A stack of quesadillas sliced into cheesy wedges of deliciousness! We snuck some veggies into the chorizo for a wholesome extra the kids won't notice!
